SCHEMA: universe/numeric_precision_policy.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.universe.numeric_precision_policy
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic numeric precision and quantization policy contracts.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record numeric_precision_policy
  required:
    - policy_id: id
    - invariant_numeric_type: enum(fixed_point|required)
    - solver_numeric_type: enum(fixed_point|deterministic_float)
    - quantization_rules: map
    - error_accumulation_strategy: id
    - extensions: map
